Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:20.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Well this whole thing started in the back of a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:24.42,英文,,0,0,0,,With this dude named Ulfric in chains
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Captain said that she wanted my head
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:32.08,英文,,0,0,0,,And things would never be the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:36.02,英文,,0,0,0,,But a fire-breathing dragon swooped on down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:40.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Hellbent on killing us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:44.54,英文,,0,0,0,,So I followed some guy and he helped me escape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Though he didn't even know me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:52.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Went on down to Whiterun town
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:56.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Joined a troop and headed out to a tower
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.60,英文,,0,0,0,,When the dragon flew in roasting me and my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:04.10,英文,,0,0,0,,And we fought him for nearly an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:09.34,英文,,0,0,0,,As he finally laid dying All my friends frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.42,英文,,0,0,0,,His soul poured right into my ass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:17.50,英文,,0,0,0,,A soldier ran up amazed and bewildered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.04,英文,,0,0,0,,And then he disbelievingly asked
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you the Dragonborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.40,英文,,0,0,0,,The Dragonborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:33.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you have that fabled power Of the shout?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.24,英文,,0,0,0,,“Fus”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Guess I’m the Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:48.28,英文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:51.54,英文,,0,0,0,,I heard this great noise up on the throat of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.74,英文,,0,0,0,,So I climbed 7.000 steps to the top
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.84,英文,,0,0,0,,There I met these four men called the Greybeards and then
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.16,英文,,0,0,0,,They put me to the test and I rocked
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:07.92,英文,,0,0,0,,They said that they wanted a taste of my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:11.34,英文,,0,0,0,,I said “fellas better get in line”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.98,英文,,0,0,0,,They taught me some words and they showed me how to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:19.04,英文,,0,0,0,,And they said you’re gonna do just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Cause you’re the Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.28,英文,,0,0,0,,The Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:32.18,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah you have that fabled power Of the shout
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:35.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.70,英文,,0,0,0,,“Fus Ro Dah”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes I’m the Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.34,英文,,0,0,0,,They tried to take my head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:46.74,英文,,0,0,0,,and they’ll rue the day we ever met
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:54.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Soon they’ll realize their big mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:59.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Cause when the time comes to make my choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:03.36,英文,,0,0,0,,To see which side will have my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:11.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Rest assured I’ll choose to make them pay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:27.12,英文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Cause when the time comes to make my choice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:35.56,英文,,0,0,0,,To see which side will have my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:42.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Each and every time I’ll choose to make them pay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.98,英文,,0,0,0,,Cause I’m the Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.44,英文,,0,0,0,,The Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I am the Dragonborn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:54.02,英文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.02,0:00:20.04,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都在那辆四轮马车上开始
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.04,0:00:24.42,中文,,0,0,0,,身边有个叫做[乌弗瑞克]的被绑老兄
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.74,中文,,0,0,0,,队长说她只想砍掉我的头
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.74,0:00:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.08,0:00:36.02,中文,,0,0,0,,但是一条火龙突然猛冲下来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.52,0:00:40.38,中文,,0,0,0,,迅猛的屠杀着我们
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.38,0:00:44.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟着那个帮我的家伙逃跑
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.10,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管他对我一无所知
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.20,0:00:52.60,中文,,0,0,0,,一直跑 直到 [雪漫城]
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.60,0:00:56.72,中文,,0,0,0,,加入一支军队 启程前往废塔
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.60,中文,,0,0,0,,那巨龙飞来 火焰烘烤我和我的伙伴
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.60,0:01:04.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我们与他搏斗了将近一个小时
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.80,0:01:09.34,中文,,0,0,0,,最后他死去了 我的伙伴们却都在燃烧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.42,中文,,0,0,0,,他的灵魂倾泻进我的身体
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.12,0:01:17.50,中文,,0,0,0,,一位战士带着惊奇跑了过来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.04,中文,,0,0,0,,他不敢相信地问
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.04,中文,,0,0,0,,"你是[龙裔]吗"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.40,中文,,0,0,0,,"龙裔?"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.16,0:01:33.62,中文,,0,0,0,,"你是否有传说中[龙吼]的力量?"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.30,中文,,0,0,0,,"全力发动它!"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,F U S
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.68,中文,,0,0,0,,也许 我是个龙裔
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.86,0:01:48.28,中文,,0,0,0,,Do vah kiin!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.28,0:01:51.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到[世界之喉]上有个声音召唤我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.74,中文,,0,0,0,,于是我爬了七千步到达山顶
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.84,中文,,0,0,0,,在那碰到四个自称[灰胡子]的老头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他们想对我测试但我不干
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.28,0:02:07.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他们说他们只想见识下我的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.92,0:02:11.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我说“排队不如去干”
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.98,中文,,0,0,0,,他们教了我个[龙吼] 并告诉我如何发动
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.98,0:02:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,然后说"你只要去做就好"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.28,中文,,0,0,0,,"因为你是[龙裔]!"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.28,中文,,0,0,0,,"龙裔!"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.14,0:02:32.18,中文,,0,0,0,,"是的,因为你有传说中[龙吼]的力量"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.78,0:02:35.46,中文,,0,0,0,,"充分发挥它的力量!"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.70,中文,,0,0,0,,Fus Ro Dah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我是龙裔!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.34,中文,,0,0,0,,这群家伙竟然想要我的头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.34,0:02:46.74,中文,,0,0,0,,再次见面他们一定会后悔
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.74,0:02:54.64,中文,,0,0,0,,他们将会意识到他们铸下了大错
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.64,0:02:59.20,中文,,0,0,0,,当我做出选择的时候到来时
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.20,0:03:03.36,中文,,0,0,0,,看看我会如何利用我的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.36,0:03:11.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我确信无疑必须让他们付出代价
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.70,0:03:27.12,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.62,中文,,0,0,0,,当我做出选择的时候到来时
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.62,0:03:35.56,中文,,0,0,0,,看看我的声音为哪方效力
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.56,0:03:42.46,中文,,0,0,0,,无论如何 我要让他们付出代价
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.98,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我是龙裔
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.44,中文,,0,0,0,,龙裔!!!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我就是龙裔!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.02,中文,,0,0,0,,
